{"tid":1122391,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂夥拍騰訊　股價大升14%","createTime":"2019-04-24T02:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T03:13:02.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"57584691e0564870358a440fad25fb5e08e52068","tid":1122391,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:32:55.000Z","msg":"騰訊（00700）旗下騰訊科技獲批代理日本任天堂遊戲主機Nintendo Switch，令任天堂可進軍中國市場，任天堂股價今飆升14%，創半年來新高。<br />\n<br />\n任天堂過去礙於法規、代理商等原因，遲遲未能幫Nintendo Switch開發中國市場，中國廣東省文化廳昨宣佈，騰訊首次獲批Nintendo Switch的遊戲代理後，受消息刺激，任天堂股價今晨曾飆升16%，最後收報升14%。<br />\n<br />\nNintendo Switch自前年推出後，迄今在全球售出逾3200萬部，投資者一度擔心後勁不繼，令股價在去年10月後便回落。隨着任天堂夥拍騰訊，遊戲機終有望進軍中國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2331636/任天堂夥拍騰訊%E3%80%80股價大升14-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2331636%2F%E4%BB%BB%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82%E5%A4%A5%E6%8B%8D%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%25E3%2580%2580%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%A4%A7%E5%8D%8714-&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubH6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=cc59132c\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2331636/任天堂夥拍騰訊%E3%80%80股價大升14-</a>"},{"pid":"bed2847a705b5443a77633318db3adeae1fc6f14","tid":1122391,"uid":20914,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"已經棄晒所有任地獄嘅驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}